Package: RWildbook
Type: Package
Title: Client for the 'Wildbook' Wildlife Photo-Identification Database
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Conservation X Labs", role = "cph"),
    person("Kirk", "Larsen", email = "georgetownpolecat@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Simon", "Bonner", email = "sbonner6@uwo.ca", role = "aut"),
    person("Xinxin", "Huang", email = "xhuan63@uwo.ca", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides an R interface to the 'Wildbook' v3 REST API
    <https://docs.wildme.org/> for wildlife photo-identification and
    mark-recapture data management. Includes functions for authentication,
    searching encounters and individuals, and constructing complex queries
    using 'OpenSearch' syntax. This package requires access to a 'Wildbook'
    v3 instance and is not compatible with legacy 'Wildbook' versions.
    This is a complete rewrite of the legacy package for the modern API.
